text:
The Arts University Bournemouth (AUB) 
Arts University Bournemouth is a further and higher education university based in Poole, Dorset, United Kingdom, specialising in art, performance, design, and media.
The Arts University Bournemouth : List of courses, Tuition fees, ranking, term dates, admissions, Open days , notable alumni. Find all the information you need to get in contact with The Arts University Bournemouth…
